Introduction

Fanxy Child is an r&b/hip hop crew comprising 6 members, Zico, Crush, Penomeco, Stay Tuned, DEAN, and Millic. They formed in 2016, with the first single considered to be from Fanxy Child, “Bermuda Triangle”.
